{"tid":321413,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"倫敦金騙案?","createTime":"2017-07-14T07:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T12:25:26.000Z","uid":45793,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"63a7c6031759b7c754f39d1bf362fd62592cf75e","tid":321413,"uid":45793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T07:57:20.000Z","msg":"小弟我機緣巧合下認識到A先生<br />\n咁A先生就同我講一個計劃，我先入3萬蚊佢幫我入17萬蚊，如果一個月內虧損就可以全數拎返我既本金3萬蚊，而蝕左既錢就佢負擔。<br />\n相反，賺左既話，當賺左20萬(戶口total 40萬)，我只要還返17萬比佢，就可以係戶口到提款。<br />\n<br />\n如果賺唔到目標價，係唔會收取手續費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打們，覺唔覺得呢個係騙案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfcd14b396604b5a4f02c24ba56abaa54142d679","tid":321413,"uid":60206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T07:59:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟我機緣巧合下認識到A先生<br />\n咁A先生就同我講一個計劃，我先入3萬蚊佢幫我入17萬蚊，如果一個月內虧損就可以全數拎返我既本金3萬蚊，而蝕左既錢就佢負擔。<br />\n相反，賺左既話，當賺左20萬(戶口total 40萬)，我只要還返17萬比佢，就可以係戶口到提款。<br />\n<br />\n如果賺唔到目標價，係唔會收取手續費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打們，覺唔覺得呢個係騙案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔通A先生真係賺得太多覺得夠? 所以先益你?"},{"pid":"8ad8e6c485937730d44297aacf080bfc893a7b45","tid":321413,"uid":45793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T08:01:04.000Z","msg":"佢話佢既職責係幫公司擴資業務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82b99fe1b60068c5e49584e8119448837131e01e","tid":321413,"uid":105590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T08:01:59.000Z","msg":"佢自己攞多3萬出黎咁難?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f66c21d00c3736a0e5372f2e925da976edd3aa23","tid":321413,"uid":45793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T08:06:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢自己攞多3萬出黎咁難?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n戶口你既，錢佢既?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55cd011b29bb711ce4ae27fa76b5b6f8f0f34dea","tid":321413,"uid":62514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T08:09:00.000Z","msg":"咁撚著數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 快啲比三皮佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67478a47b5cd6ae0ac74b1ad3ca80559ee5b2de4","tid":321413,"uid":45793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T08:26:26.000Z","msg":"認真問阿巴打們"},{"pid":"4c9a344941b2d705e18de15cbf851b8118d7a97e","tid":321413,"uid":45793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T09:17:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a9074240b093727806892a6a69963cbcfbe904f","tid":321413,"uid":62514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T09:20:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真問阿巴打們</blockquote><br />\n屌你唔撚係信下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d6ad95006d53c1296b098a29d567c4b71740672","tid":321413,"uid":22696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T09:22:19.000Z","msg":"快啲俾三皮佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢益左第二個你就走寶"},{"pid":"4be94213fdadcc318257d18aeaa20f9521330641","tid":321413,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:48:51.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"36804fb68fca02f587e8646e017b638814d34b77","tid":321413,"uid":771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:50:48.000Z","msg":"所以話呢d 老千係香港呃極都仲係有蠢撚送上門"},{"pid":"ef7167ce0c26e4ea70f89dda7b93f49d75ff4c16","tid":321413,"uid":113775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:53:41.000Z","msg":"唔好信<br />\n冇咁好嫁，巴打小心中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56f6fd6970b785cf4f2163cdff284a89fa76ff02","tid":321413,"uid":45793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T12:03:01.000Z","msg":"已推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝巴打<br />\n比貪念沖芬頭腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0fc37f9701a97f8977cea70f58ad76cbe077070","tid":321413,"uid":116166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T21:19:30.000Z","msg":"我知成件事點解<br />\n首先佢地會同你講入3萬，之後佢幫你出17萬其實佢根本唔洗拎錢出黎，因為佢只係需要打條數入你炒金Account ，之後可以做幾個炒賣記錄，等你認為賺左錢就比埋果17萬落去。博你個心雄左，之後再繼續trade 咁佢就可以做單。咁就可以賺你錢。<br />\n<br />\n利申:行業元老，但從不 偷呃柺騙"},{"pid":"42280021e7bbd19492aa34d29617e6cf6e9359c7","tid":321413,"uid":34256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T21:37:23.000Z","msg":"同佢講投資15萬就夠<br />\n有賺先比錢你 冇就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢仲出少2萬"},{"pid":"b77d892e48c7ca5000d3d299c4ba00e64dcbd0d8","tid":321413,"uid":144101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T12:25:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝巴打<br />\n比貪念沖芬頭腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/202447_fe8af67d5787314769d5e23f1bf7935a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F202447_fe8af67d5787314769d5e23f1bf7935a.jpg&h=5bf76f61&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/202502_c9dff918caab544e1e12997c3a16f878.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F202502_c9dff918caab544e1e12997c3a16f878.jpg&h=6ba7c3ef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.ese